item.title: Changelog
item.description: It makes it easier for users and contributors to see the most notable changes that have been made on HotelX product. All notable changes on our platform will be documented on this page. 2018-11-27 Ambiguous warning message in Book when supplier has not returned price Removed error nodes from Groups and Organization nodes Removed log if amount is 0 in Fees node 2018-11-20 Added geonames in Hotel-List Added access code in book log in some special cases of commission Partially synchronous resource caches in Hotel-Quote, Hotel-Book, Hotel-Cancel, Hotel-Booking 2018-11-19 Fix Stats Fix Hotels requested stats in Access and Transaction spans where the count wasn’t correct in some cases Margin plugin compares net commission in order to decide discarding or mantaining an option.
